title: JUICY CONFESSIONS!
description:
In this episode Jessi and Stew read confessions from their followers and then spill the juiciest confessions they have been keeping secret... did you know Stew was almost hired onto a reality show? And that Jessi was her mom's secret stalker for almost 2 years? Listen to the episode to find out more details!
